xyz.kotlout.kotlout.model.user

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.kotlout.kotlout.model.user.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A class representing a single user of the app. As there is no way to make accounts, this also corresponds directly to a device on which the app is installed.
    See Also:

        Instantiates a new User with information about that user. All fields can optionally be set to null except uuid.
        Parameters:
        firstName - the user's first name
        lastName - the user's last name
        email - the user's email
        phoneNumber - the user's phone number
        uuid - the uuid to assign to the user
